ttp_template:
<group name="chassis_ha_state_configured_state_effective_state_slot">
Chassis HA State: {{CHASSIS_HA_STATE | ORPHRASE}}
Sync Status: {{SYNC_STATUS | ORPHRASE}}
 Status: {{STATUS | ORPHRASE}}
Slot: {{SLOT | ORPHRASE}}
 Configured State: {{CONFIGURED_STATE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:

-----

textfsm_template:
Value CHASSIS_HA_STATE (\w+)
Value SYNC_STATUS (\w+)
Value SLOT (\w+-\d+)
Value CONFIGURED_STATE (\w+)
Value EFFECTIVE_STATE (\w+)
Value STATUS (\w+)

Start
  ^Chassis\sHA\sState:\s${CHASSIS_HA_STATE}\s*$$
  ^Sync\sStatus:\s${SYNC_STATUS}\s*$$
  ^-{5}$$
  ^Slot:\s${SLOT}\s*$$
  ^\sConfigured\sState:\s${CONFIGURED_STATE}\s*$$
  ^\sEffective\sState:\s${EFFECTIVE_STATE}\s*$$
  ^\sStatus:\s${STATUS}\s*$$ -> Record
